name: Urban Warrior
overview: Urban Warrior is a 1 or 2 player (co-op) vertically scrolling shooter for the Commodore 64. It was developed by Video Images Software using the Shoot 'em Up Construction Kit and released into the public domain in 1988. The file on Gb64 has two versions, one being the original 1988 version, and the other being a version from 2015. The only difference, however, is that the 2015 release has title music and a different title screen, the gameplay is no different.
